| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0261 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 1f369aa5-f22d-5544-97f7-9def3e5e44bf"
